### Time Slots

```css
.zc-hour-block {
  height: 80px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  position: relative;
}

/* Linha de meia hora (::after) */
.zc-hour-block::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  top: 50%;
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--color-border);
  opacity: 0.4;
}

/* Slot clicável (15min cada) */
.zc-time-slot {
  flex: 1 auto;
  border: none;
  width: 100%;
  background-color: transparent;
  cursor: pointer;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

/* Slots em horário de trabalho */
.zc-time-slot--working {
  background-color: var(--color-card);  /* #ffffff */
}

/* Hover em horário de trabalho */
.zc-time-slot--working:hover {
  background-color: var(--color-accent);  /* #eef2ff */
}

/* Hover fora do horário */
.zc-time-slot:not(.zc-time-slot--working):hover {
  background-color: rgba(237, 238, 242, 0.8);
}

/* Label de hora ao hover */
.zc-time-slot__label {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--color-muted-foreground);
  font-weight: 500;
  visibility: hidden;
}
.zc-time-slot:hover .zc-time-slot__label {
  visibility: visible;
}
```

