## 5.3 Eventos e Agendamentos

```css
/* Evento base */
.zc-event {
  position: absolute;
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 4px 8px;
  font-size: 12px;
  overflow: hidden;
  cursor: pointer;
  z-index: 5;
  box-shadow: rgba(0,0,0,0.1) 0 1px 3px;
  transition: box-shadow 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
  /* Borda esquerda colorida */
  border-top: none;
  border-right: none;
  border-bottom: none;
  border-left: 3px solid;  /* cor definida por variante */
}

.zc-event:hover {
  box-shadow: rgba(0,0,0,0.18) 0 3px 10px;
  transform: translate(1px);
}

/* Título do evento */
.zc-event__title {
  font-weight: 600;
  display: block;
  white-space: nowrap;
  overflow: hidden;
  text-overflow: ellipsis;
}

/* Horário do evento */
.zc-event__time {
  display: block;
  font-weight: 400;
  opacity: 0.85;
  font-size: 11px;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

/* Evento agendado manualmente (verde) */
.zc-event--manual {
  background-color: rgb(198, 241, 211);
  color: oklch(0.25 0.08 155);
  border-left-color: oklch(0.6 0.15 155);
}

/* Evento padrão (azul) */
.zc-event--default {
  background-color: oklch(0.92 0.04 264);
  color: rgb(13, 39, 105);
  border-left-color: var(--color-primary);
}
```

